---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /proizvodi/
title: "SMIŽ - Proizvodi"
description: "SMIŽ - Program proizvoda: automatska, bolnička, unutrašnja, industrijska i garažna vrata, kao i zaštitna rešenja od jonizujućeg zračenja."
ogTitle: "SMIŽ - Proizvodi"
ogDescription: "Pregled kompletnog SMIŽ programa proizvoda i specijalizovanih rešenja za različite tipove objekata i namena."
ogImage: "/images/logo-mini.png"
pageType: products
isProductPage: false
---

{# --- HERO SEKCIJA --- #}
<section class="products-header">
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="breadcrumb">
            <a href="/">Početna</a> / <span>Proizvodi</span>
        </nav>
        <h1>Naša <span class="text-accent">rešenja</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-lead">Sveobuhvatan program vrata i zaštitnih sistema za medicinske, industrijske i rezidencijalne objekte.</p>
    </div>
</section>

{# --- KATALOG GRID --- #}
<section class="section catalog-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="catalog-grid">
            {% for product in site.navProducts %}
            <article class="product-item">
                <div class="product-card">
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <span class="card-category">Kategorija {{ loop.index }}</span>
                        <h3>{{ product.label }}</h3>
                        <p>Profesionalna rešenja, tehnička dokumentacija i stručna ugradnja za {{ product.label | lower }}.</p>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                            <a href="{{ product.href }}" class="btn-link">
                                Detalji proizvoda 
                                <span class="arrow">→</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{# --- GLOBALNI CTA --- #}
<section class="section-alt help-cta">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="help-box">
            <div class="help-text">
                <h2>Niste sigurni šta vam je potrebno?</h2>
                <p>Naš tim inženjera će vam pomoći da odaberete vrata koja najbolje odgovaraju vašem projektu i budžetu.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/kontakt/" class="btn btn-dark">Konsultujte se sa nama</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script id="productsData" type="application/json">
[
{% for product in site.products %}
  {
    "title": {{ product.label | dump | safe }},
    "description": {{ product.description | dump | safe }},
    "image": {{ product.image | dump | safe }},
    "link": {{ product.href | dump | safe }}
  }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
]
</script>

<style>
    :root {
        --accent: #005e83;
        --dark: #1a1a1a;
        --light: #f8fafc;
        --border: #e2e8f0;
        --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    .text-accent { color: var(--accent); }

    /* Header */
    .products-header { padding: 80px 0 40px; background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #999; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .breadcrumb a { color: var(--dark); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }
    .products-header h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
    .hero-lead { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; max-width: 600px; margin-top: 1rem; }

    /* Catalog Grid */
    .catalog-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .product-card {
        height: 100%;
        background: white;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        transition: var(--transition);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .product-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--accent);
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .card-content { padding: 3rem 2.5rem; flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    
    .card-category { 
        font-size: 0.75rem; 
        font-weight: 800; 
        text-transform: uppercase; 
        color: var(--accent); 
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        display: block;
    }

    .product-card h3 { 
        font-size: 1.8rem; 
        font-weight: 800; 
        margin-bottom: 1rem; 
        color: var(--dark);
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .product-card p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem; flex-grow: 1; }

    .btn-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--dark);
        font-weight: 800;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        transition: var(--transition);
    }

    .product-card:hover .btn-link { color: var(--accent); }
    .arrow { transition: var(--transition); }
    .product-card:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(5px); }

    /* Help CTA */
    .help-box {
        background: var(--dark);
        color: white;
        padding: 4rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    .help-text h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .help-text p { opacity: 0.7; font-size: 1.1rem; }

    .btn-dark {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
        padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        transition: var(--transition);
        white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--dark); transform: translateY(-3px); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .catalog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .help-box { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
        .card-content { padding: 2rem; }
    }
</style>